# local-only demo/test credentials — never commit (repo may be public)
DEMO_CREDENTIALS.md

# Docs are local-only by default (business/planning/compliance), EXCEPT the
# development docs explicitly re-included below. Ignore the folder's *contents*
# (docs/*, not docs/) so these negations can take effect.
docs/*
!docs/RUN_LOCAL_DEMO.md
!docs/POS_Prototype_Roadmap.md

